Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.04,0:00:09.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诞生了无限膨胀的\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}giving birth to an endless expanding existence...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.25,0:00:11.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,时间 空间和物质\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}of time, space, and matter.
