Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.13,0:00:16.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,超越了客观认知极限\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}beyond the limits of our existence...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.05,0:00:18.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那地方我们称之为"宇宙"\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}in a place we call "The Universe."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.39,0:00:24.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,假如预测到要起狂风\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}What ifthe forecast predicted high winds...
