Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.32,0:00:34.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晚上下起倾盆的硫酸雨\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}An evening downpour of sulfuric acid rain...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.28,0:00:44.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或刮起了持续300年 两倍地球大小范围的飓风又当如何呢？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}or a hurricane two times the size of Earth lasting 300 years?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.42,0:00:50.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不是科幻素材电影\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}This is not the stuff of a science fiction movie.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.30,0:00:53.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而是来自宇宙的天气预报\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}These are actual weather reports from around the universe...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.97,0:00:56.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是地球天气的极限\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and it's Earth's weather to the extreme.
