Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.56,0:01:08.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最古怪 最疯狂的天气\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}weirdest, and wildest weather the universe creates.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.19,0:01:13.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请系好你的安全带 开始崎岖之旅\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Fasten your seatbelts. lt's going to be a bumpy ride.
