Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.22,0:21:11.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些因素结合起来可以理想地模拟\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Combined, these elements perfectly mimic...
