Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.45,0:21:32.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阳光照射 加热地面\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Sunlight comes down and heats up the surface...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.12,0:21:37.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而热量需要通过热气团来对流\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and that heat needs to be convected away...by hot blobs of air.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.54,0:21:41.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,热气团从地面离开后 空气会被吸进去\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}As these hot blobs move away from the surface, air is drawn in.
