Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.05,0:21:47.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,空气旋转会越来越快\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}that air spins up, moving faster and faster...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.30,0:21:48.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在高速带动下\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and with those higher speeds...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.72,0:21:50.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会将尘埃卷入大气层\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}kicks dust up into the atmosphere.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.89,0:21:53.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,随着热气团在地表的移动\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}As this hot blob of air moves away from the surface...
