Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.77,0:22:01.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宽度通常有数百米\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and widths of typically a hundred meters...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.06,0:22:02.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会变得更强\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and will get stronger...
