Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.05,0:22:30.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"我居然被尘暴击倒了"\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}"l just got bowled over by a dust devil."
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.89,0:22:32.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那种情况是不会发生的\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}That's not going to happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.06,0:22:43.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最后盘点的星际龙卷风事件是个真正的谜团\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The final galactic tornado event on the countdown is a true mystery.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.48,0:22:48.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来龙卷风形成背后的理论颠倒了\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}And it turns theories behind tornado formation upside down.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.09,0:23:08.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最后盘点的龙卷风是个双重麻烦\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The final tornado on the countdown is double trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.10,0:23:21.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,金星 曾经被视为浪漫之星\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Venus, once viewed as a romantic planet...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.19,0:23:24.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有着非常可怕的天气情况\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}has some truly horrific weather conditions.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.11,0:23:32.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,温室效应肆虐带来的闷热\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Oppressive heat with a greenhouse effect gone amok...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.99,0:23:37.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这颗行星在不断设法自我冷却\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}this is one planet that is constantly trying to cool itself off...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.29,0:23:38.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有得逞\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}with no success.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.17,0:23:48.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,金星是个迷人的不友好之地\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Venus is a fascinatingly hostile place.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.01,0:23:53.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它非常不友好 以至于即使我们把机器送上去\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}lt's so hostile that even our machines that we send there...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.72,0:23:57.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,工作上几分钟 零件就会融化掉了\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}they work for, like, a few minutes, and then the components melt.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.27,0:24:04.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由于持续的高温 风暴始终存在于金星上\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}As a result ofthis constant heat, storms are always present on Venus...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.31,0:24:09.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就产生了一个从未见过的最有趣的漩涡\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and this makes for one ofthe most interesting vortex events ever observed.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.65,0:24:14.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一对巨大的 上下颠倒的龙卷风\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}There's a giant, upside down, twin tornado...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.41,0:24:16.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,固定不变地存在于金星的极地\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}permanently existing at the pole ofVenus.
