Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.00,0:24:26.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,科学家一直致力于了解颠倒运行于\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}scientists have struggled to understand the twin vortexes...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.71,0:24:30.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其南极地区的孪生漩涡\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}running upside down at her south polar region.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.34,0:24:32.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,某种意义上 它是个颠倒的龙卷风\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}ln a sense, it's an upside down tornado...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.80,0:24:38.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为空气是从漩涡的顶部漏向地面\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}because the air is funneling from the top part of that spiral...down towards the ground...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.26,0:24:40.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而地球上典型的龙卷风\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}whereas a typical tornado on Earth...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.56,0:24:43.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你会看到是通过漏斗往上升的\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}you think of the air kind of rising up through the funnel.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.73,0:24:46.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奇怪的是那是个双龙卷风\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}And the strange thing is that it's a double vortex.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.56,0:24:48.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是 反映出两个巨大的龙卷风\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}That is, picture two giant tornadoes...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.40,0:24:50.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像是互相缠绕着\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}sort of rotating around each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.15,0:24:53.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可以看到两个波瓣 它分成了两半\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}And you can see the two lobes, the two halves of it here.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.66,0:25:02.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,科学家认为漩涡是大气中热传导导致的\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Scientists believe the vortexes...are a result of heat transfer in the atmosphere.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.75,0:25:05.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,热从金星的赤道升起\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Heat rises atVenus' equator...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.12,0:25:08.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后下沉到星球最冷的地方\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}then sinks at the coolest section of the planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.13,0:25:10.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宛如浴缸放水 其中的水…\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Like a bathtub draining, where the water is...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.84,0:25:15.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,水流集中排放 就会形成旋转\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}That flow is concentrated on the drain...and it leads to this spinning motion.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.72,0:25:19.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为何它会是双龙卷风 我们确实无法理解\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Why it's a double vortex, we don't really understand that.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.10,0:25:20.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它始终是个谜\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}lt's still mysterious.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.60,0:25:24.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个风暴在火星上很庞大\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}This storm is an enormous presence on Venus.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.56,0:25:27.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有数千英里宽\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}lt's thousands of miles across.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.10,0:25:30.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其产生的风达到了时速数百英里\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The winds it generates are hundreds of miles an hour...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.19,0:25:34.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些漩涡是金星上的固定标志\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and these vortexes are a permanent fixture on Venus.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.41,0:25:48.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太空中的天气千奇百怪\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Weather takes many strange forms in space...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.30,0:25:54.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,包括下雨\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}even rain.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.89,0:26:03.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过其他行星的大气层\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}But other planets have atmospheres...
